			<h1>üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Lew Lew Lemon Fan!</h1><!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coming Soon - F1 Vancouver</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .background-image {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Lewis_Hamilton_2023_Saudi_Arabian_Grand_Prix.jpg/1280px-Lewis_Hamilton_2023_Saudi_Arabian_Grand_Prix.jpg'); /* A publicly available image of Lewis Hamilton */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            filter: blur(8px); /* Adjust blur strength as needed */
            -webkit-filter: blur(8px); /* Safari support */
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .overlay {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* Dark overlay for better text readability */
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .content-box {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo img {
            width: 80px; /* Adjust logo size */
            height: auto;
            filter: invert(100%); /* Make logo white if it's dark */
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            color: #4CAF50; /* A green color for links */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #ccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background-image"></div>
    <div class="overlay"></div>

    <div class="content-box">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ca/F1_logo.svg/1000px-F1_logo.svg.png" alt="F1 Logo">
        </div>
        <h1>COMING SOON</h1>
        <p>
            Get ready for the ultimate F1 experience in Vancouver! Join our community for updates and discussions.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/vanf1/" target="_blank">Join F1 Vancouver on Facebook</a>
        </p>
        <div class="contact-info">
            For details on purchasing the domain, please contact: <br>
            <a href="mailto:obrien.kevan@gmail.com">obrien.kevan@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
